<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Do not be angry and frustrated.</para>

<para style="q1">Do not worry. This only makes trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Evildoers will be cut off,</para>

<para style="q1">but those who wait for Yahweh will inherit the land.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />In a little while the evil man will disappear;</para>

<para style="q1">you will look at his place, but he will be gone.</para>
